To get pixlotto running:


1. install MySQL and tomcat8

2. import the pixlotto_2017-09-17.sql: (https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/5.7/en/creating-database.html)
2.1 start mysql: mysql -u user -p password
2.2 create pixlottoDB: mysql> CREATE DATABASE pixlottoDB; 
2.3 switch to pixlottoDB: mysql> USE menagerie
2.4 load the file: mysql> SOURCE [path to]/pixlotto_2017-09-17.sql

3. copy the extracted archive (pixlotto folder) in the tomcat8  webapps folder. In my ubuntu linux it is: /var/lib/tomcat8/webapps

4. start tomcat8: in Ubuntu run the script:  /etc/init.d/tomcat8 start 

5. point the browser to localhost:8080/pixlotto/main

6. hpefully you are done 




